title: Books, and type, and decorated papers and other really boring stuff
content: I've finally started to sort through the 1GB+ of picture files I brought back -- it will likely take awhile to get the rest up, but in the meantime and in between time, you can see some stuff [here](http://web.archive.org/web/20131020111757/http:/flickr.com/photos/lasquetipress/collections/72157604935245347/).
author: Linda Cunningham
